# MoveToNamedTarget Service Definition
#
# Commands MoveIt to move to a named target (e.g., "home", "ready") defined in the SRDF.
#
# Request:
#   - target_name: Name of the SRDF group state to move to.
#   - execute: If true, plan and execute. If false, plan only.
#
# Response:
#   - success: True if planning (and execution if requested) succeeded.
#   - message: Human-readable result/diagnostic message.

string target_name
bool execute
---
bool success
string message
